title: Puss in Boots: The Last Wish
description: Embark on an animated journey filled with action, adventure, and comedy for the whole family. Join Puss in Boots as he sets out on his last thrilling quest.

title: Avatar: The Way of Water
description: Immerse yourself in a visually stunning science fiction adventure that transports you to the mystical world of Pandora. Join the journey of discovery in the search for the Way of Water.

title: M3GAN
description: Prepare for a thrilling ride through the realms of science fiction, horror, and comedy. Follow the story of M3GAN, a technological marvel with a mischievous mind of her own.

title: Troll
description: Enter a world of fantasy and adventure where trolls roam free and heroes rise to the challenge. Join the quest to defeat evil and restore peace to the land.

title: Black Adam
description: Experience the awe-inspiring journey of Black Adam, a powerful force for justice in a world of fantasy and science fiction. Witness the rise of a hero in a time of darkness.

title: Avatar
description: Embark on an epic fantasy adventure to the distant planet of Pandora, where wonders and dangers await at every turn. Join the Na'vi in their fight to protect their home.

title: Roald Dahl's Matilda the Musical
description: Step into a world of magic and wonder where anything is possible. Join Matilda on her journey of self-discovery as she unlocks the secrets of her extraordinary abilities.

title: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever
description: Journey to the futuristic world of Wakanda, where tradition meets technology and heroes rise to defend their homeland. Experience the power of Wakanda forever.

title: Strange World
description: Embark on a thrilling family adventure where science fiction meets animation in a world like no other. Discover the wonders of a Strange World filled with mystery and excitement.

title: The Woman King
description: Witness the epic tale of The Woman King, a fearless warrior who defied the odds to protect her people and forge her own destiny. Experience the power of courage and resilience.
